doc.previous: In February 2014 the Jakarta Government started providing double decker bus tours that offers sightseeing in Central Jakarta The buses route covers tourist attractions such as Monas Istiqlal Mosque the Cathedral National Museum Sarinah and Plaza Indonesia as well as Grand Indonesia shopping centers 103
